# Agent skills installed into ~/.agents/skills via `npx skills add ...`.
#
# Format (one per line, comments with #):
#   <source>                       install every skill from the source
#   <source> --skill <name>        install one named skill from the source
#
# `<source>` accepts the same forms `npx skills add` takes: a full GitHub URL,
# or shorthand `<owner>/<repo>`. Run `bash agents/install.sh` to apply.

